casebody.data:
Phyllis Dorothy MABBETT, petitioner,
v.
COMMISSIONER OF INTERNAL REVENUE. No. 15-6491. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 9, 2015.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until November 30, 2015, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in *497compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
